methods.binMax:
Gets the max value of the bin at index.

:param index: (long) - index
:return: (double) max value of the bin specified by index
methods.binMin:
Gets the min value of the bin at index.

:param index: (long) - index
:return: (double) min value of the bin specified by index
methods.index:
Gets the index of the bin the value lies in.

:param value: (double) - value
:return: (long) max value of the bin specified by index

text: DiscretizedRange where all bins are equal length.
